short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension calculates the total price of the products in the cart on Aliexpress with the number of items

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Calculate the total price of all the orders made on the ali-express website, so that you can know just how much money you're spending on the ali express website as we all buy small ticket items which really add up over time!
MIT Github is linked
https://github.com/oslohes123/ali-express-extension
